  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Busha / Senior Frontend Engineer"
      subtitle="MAY 2022 - PRESENT,  LAGOS, NIGERIA"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4">
        <li>
          Optimized Busha Exchange platform for accessibility enabling 100k+
          users to trade and exchange cryptocurrency seamlessly.
        </li>
        <li>
          Developed crypto-based Busha Commerce adopted by 100k + businesses.
        </li>
        <li>
          Delivered two critical back-office systems ("Backups") that enhanced
          customer operations efficiency, reducing resolution times by 30%.
        </li>
        <li>
          Led a team of 8 engineers, establishing coding standards, conducting
          code reviews, and optimizing development cycles, resulting in a 25%
          reduction in deployment times.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4 italic">
        Core Technologies: React.js, Tailwind CSS, Flutter DDP, Node, Jes
      </p>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Ubiscore / Frontend Engineer"
      subtitle="APRIL  2022 - JANUARY 2023, BERLIN, GERMANY"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4">
        <li>
          Contributed to the development of the world’s first AI-powered
          platform for data privacy scoring.
        </li>
        <li>
          Authored the most pull requests and became the largest contributor to
          the codebase, playing a key role in implementing features, resolving
          issues, and maintaining code quality.
        </li>
        <li>
          Ensured code base excellence by participating in code review sessions,
          providing feedback to uphold coding standards and improve
          productivity.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4 italic">
        Core Technologies: Next.js, GraphQL, SaaS, TypeScript, React.
      </p>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Prunedge / Senior Frontend Engineer"
      subtitle="MAY 2023 - JULY 2023,  CARLIFORNIA, USA"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4">
        <li>
          Developed enterprise-grade HRM software for leading banks,providing
          robust employee management capabilities.
        </li>
        <li>
          Led the front-end development of a Customer Relationship Management
          (CRM) delivering a user-friendly and efficient platform still in
          active use.
        </li>
        <li>
          Introduced innovative department patterns to boost team efficiency and
          minimise bugs.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4 italic">
        Core Technologies: React.js, TypeScript, Redux, React Query,
        Material-UI.
      </p>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Metricks / Frontend Engineer"
      subtitle="MAY 2023 - JULY 2023,  LONDON, UNITED KINGDOM"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4">
        <li>
          Solely developed a high-performance platform enabling users to create
          and manage affiliate marketing campaigns, attracting thousands of
          onboarded users within weeks of launch.
        </li>
        <li>
          Spearheaded the migration from vanilla JavaScript to TypeScript,
          introducing a new front-end architecture that enhanced scalability and
          reduced bug occurrences, resulting in a 30% improvement in development
          efficiency.
        </li>
        <li>
          Designed and integrated a blog feature using Sanity CMS, enabling
          dynamic content updates and streamlining marketing efforts.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4 italic">
        Core Technologies: Next.js, TypeScript, Sanity, Tailwind CSS.
      </p>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Turing / Senior Frontend Engineer"
      subtitle="OCT 2022 - NOV 2022, PALO ALTO, USA"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc ml-4">
        <li>
          Contributed to the design and implementation scalable, user-friendly
          interfaces to ensure seamless chatbot interactions for customers at
          XAPP AI.
        </li>
        <li>
          Leveraged technologies testing framework such as React.js, Redux,
          GraphQL to optimize the chatbot for efficiency.
        </li>
        <li>
          Interfaced with senior engineers to boost proficiency and improve team
          relations.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4 italic">Core Technologies: React.js, TypeScript, Redux.</p>
    </TimeLineElement>
