        TypeScript that connects parents with K-12 private schools across
        Africa. It features school search, comparison, enrollment support, and
        affordable education financing options. The platform serves parents,
        schools, vendors, and lenders, creating an easy-to-use ecosystem that
        simplifies school selection and financing through a modern, responsive
        frontend.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://fedworks.africa/"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-lg font-bold text-primary">Fedworks</a
      >
      <p>
        Created a visually engaging portfolio website highlighting the company’s
        past projects, brand influences, and portfolio, enhancing audience
        engagement and brand visibility.
      </p>
    </li>
